description: This Java class 'Generated' serves as a container for information about a generated source file, including its class name, package, variable name, and source file location.

classes.name: Generated
classes.description: A class that encapsulates metadata about a generated Java source file.

methods.name: getVarName
methods.description: Returns the variable name associated with the generated source.

methods.name: setVarName
methods.description: Sets the variable name associated with the generated source.

methods.name: getClassName
methods.description: Returns the class name of the generated source.

methods.name: setClassName
methods.description: Sets the class name of the generated source.

methods.name: getPackageName
methods.description: Returns the package name of the generated source.

methods.name: setPackageName
methods.description: Sets the package name of the generated source.

methods.name: getSrcFile
methods.description: Returns the File object representing the source file.

methods.name: setSrcFile
methods.description: Sets the File object representing the source file.
